    public class MaterialDocViewer
extends gwt.material.design.client.base.MaterialWidget
    A document viewer for your word, excel, powerpoint, pdf and other supported file types .
    Note that this viewer only work with public files.

    XML Namespace Declaration

     xmlns:ma='urn:import:gwt.material.design.addins.client'

    UiBinder Usage:

     <ma:docviewer.MaterialDocViewer url="http://infolab.stanford.edu/pub/papers/google.pdf" embedded="true"/>
    Author:
    kevzlou7979
    See Also:
    Doc Viewer
